{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "a13b7cd9-f5a7-4857-a9a6-a71c1e7699fc", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a13b7cd9-f5a7-4857-a9a6-a71c1e7699fc@1.pkg/1772597613253/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597613667", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a13b7cd9-f5a7-4857-a9a6-a71c1e7699fc@1.pkg/1772597613253/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597613667"}, "identifier": "a13b7cd9-f5a7-4857-a9a6-a71c1e7699fc", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查如何在奉献社会中成就精彩人生。​</b></span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：黄文秀放弃城市工作机会，扎根基层奉献，并未体现对个人利益的追求，A错误。</b></span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：黄文秀主动到贫困村工作，带领村民发展产业、奉献青春，用实际行动诠释了通过奉献社会实现人生价值的意义，B正确。​</b></span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：未提及她在过程中遭遇的挫折及意志锻炼，C错误。​</b></span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：黄文秀放弃舒适的城市工作，选择到基层奋斗，并非安于现状，D错误。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选B。</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）&ldquo;七一勋章&rdquo;获得者黄文秀毕业后放弃城市工作机会，主动请缨到贫困村担